textAfterTable: Set Description from Beckett Database Released in October of 2004 under the name Bowman Rookies and Stars again this year, packs contained an assortment of cards from both Bowman and Bowman Chrome, therefore they have been designated as such. Both sets contain 156 cards where cards 1-110 feature veteran players, cards 111-146 feature rookies, and card numbers 147-156 feature autographed rookie cards inserted at one in 105 packs for Bowman and are sequentially numbered to 250 for Bowman Chrome. All cards have gray borders, but the veteran players have red accents along the side borders and the rookies have blue accents. Boxes contained 24 packs of seven cards (four Bowman, two Bowman Chrome and one Bowman Gold Parallel) that carried a SRP of $4.00.
